data.description:
SELLER IS OFFERING $5000 IN CONCESSIONS TO BE USED FOR CLOSING COSTS OR BUY DOWN!!! 
This is your chance to have that serene country life you’ve always dreamed of! This 4400 sq foot ranch style 4 bedroom 2 bath home sits on 35 acres and hosts a huge 100 sq foot chicken coop that houses 35 chickens and 4 roosters just waiting to meet you as well as a fully fenced pasture with horse stalls. When you enter this well cared for home you are greeted with high ceilings, wonderful natural light and an open floor plan. The primary bedroom has a 3/4 ensuite with large custom tiled shower and walk in closet, 2nd bedroom also has a walk in closet. Updated full hall bath. Kitchen has abundant counter & cabinet space, pantry, island and breakfast nook as well as a formal dining area. Mud/laundry room off back entrance has plenty of shelving and storage. Sit and unwind on your back patio or soak in your hot tub under the stars. With 360 degree views you can enjoy the sun rising and the sun setting on your deck. No matter which direction you look from this property there is endless countryside and sky. Raised garden beds allow you grow vegetables, herbs and flowers easily.
New paint and flooring throughout. Roof, gutters, down spouts, exterior paint and double pain windows are all 2 yrs old. The full unfinished walk out basement is currently a shop area but is a blank slate waiting to be designed. Schools are listed as Agate School district but Deer Trail offers open enrollment.  
Please consider driving a FWD vehicle (or AWD at minimum) to view this property. The recent rainfall has made the roads a bit rough.
